Create retrieval mechanism fot fellowship applications (entity order-lab\orderflex\src\App\FellAppBundle\Entity\FellowshipApplication.php)
via API using a hash key $hashkey="jshdjhds".
Caller server send request to Remote server and the remote server send back JSON response.
Use only order-lab\orderflex\src\App\FellAppBundle\Controller\FellAppRetrievalController.php to implement Caller and Remote server API controllers,
do not change other files.
1) Caller server makes an API call to remote server via url https://view.online/fellowship-applications/download-application-data/$hashkey
2) Remote server receives this API call
3) Remote server create a xlsx file containing all fields in FellowshipApplication and $hashkey and send it back via JSON response
4) Remote server send back JSON data to the caller server
5) Caller server receive JSON from the remote server
6) Caller server authenticate $hashkey
7) Caller server receive xlsx file and store it locally in order-lab\orderflex\public\Uploaded\fellapp\Spreadsheets



